participants_seed.csv
docs/pilot-data-snapshot-*/assessment_responses.csv
docs/pilot-data-snapshot-*/intake_responses.csv
docs/pilot-data-snapshot-*/pilot_feedback.csv
docs/pilot-data-snapshot-*/chat_logs.csv

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
